<li><i>Bridge Whist</i> by C.J. Melrose. New York, Charles Scribner's Sons. (1901)</li>
<li><i>Elwell's Advanced Bridge</i> by J.B. Elwell. London, George Newnes. (5th ed., 1905)</li>
<li><i>Bridge and Auction Bridge</i> by "Valet de Pique". London, Eveleigh Nash. (1912)</li>
<li><i>Royal Auction Bridge</i> by Ernest Bergholt. London, George Routledge &amp; Sons. (1915?)</li>
<li><i>The Mad World of Bridge</i> by <a href="/wiki/Jack_Olsen" title="Jack Olsen">Jack Olsen</a>. New York, Holt, Rinehart &amp; Winston. (1960)</li>
<li><i>The Walk of the Oysters</i> by Rex Mackey, London, W.H.Allen, 1964.</li>
<li><i>Bridge Is My Game</i> by <a href="/wiki/Jack_Olsen" title="Jack Olsen">Jack Olsen</a> with <a href="/wiki/Charles_Goren" title="Charles Goren">Charles Goren</a>. New York, Doubleday. (1965)</li>
</ul>
